3. Concepts

Subtypes
  • CallActivity
  • SubProcess
  • Task

  • activity_isForCompensation
  • activity_startQuantity
Relations with source
  • Activity â Activity_BoundaryEventRefs â BoundaryEvent
  • Activity â Activity_DataInputAssociations â DataInputAssociation
  • Activity â Activity_DataOutputAssociations â DataOutputAssociation
  • Activity â Activity_Default â SequenceFlow
  • Activity â Activity_IoSpecification â InputOutputSpecification
  • Activity â Activity_LoopCharacteristics â LoopCharacteristics
  • Activity â Activity_Properties â Property
  • Activity â Activity_Resources â ResourceRole
